    "title": "Immediate Requirement Medical Officer at Merck India Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Medical Officer with drive and ambition, Merck India Ventures Solutions in Faridabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Merck India Ventures Solutions:\nMerck India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Merck India Ventures Solutions!",
